1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=Saat Aku Bertemu Kamu=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:15,000
=Episod 8=

3
00:00:17,039 --> 00:00:19,260
Kamu berdua pegawai kanan
Biro Pintu Gerbang.

4
00:00:19,760 --> 00:00:23,280
Tapi kamu bertengkar macam samseng
di depan anak buah.

5
00:00:23,962 --> 00:00:25,043
Tak boleh diterima.

6
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:27,879
Ampun, tuan.

7
00:00:28,760 --> 00:00:29,399
Datuk,

8
00:00:29,679 --> 00:00:31,440
Mao Buyu jelas hilang pertimbangan.

9
00:00:31,440 --> 00:00:32,799
Dia melindungi Tupai Jed.

10
00:00:32,799 --> 00:00:33,439
Wushuang!

11
00:00:33,520 --> 00:00:35,479
Selagi belum disabitkan,
kau tak boleh tuduh Chang.

12
00:00:35,479 --> 00:00:35,840
Saya...

13
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:36,479
Cukup.

14
00:00:37,320 --> 00:00:39,100
Jaga adab dan tenang
dalam kes besar.

15
00:00:39,600 --> 00:00:40,479
Aku dah serahkan laporan.

16
00:00:40,840 --> 00:00:41,600
Dalam tiga hari,

17
00:00:41,679 --> 00:00:44,119
Timbalan Menteri sendiri
akan soal siasat Lin Xin'er.

18
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:47,479
Kebenaran akan terbongkar nanti.

19
00:00:47,479 --> 00:00:48,799
Timbalan Menteri ambil alih

20
00:00:48,799 --> 00:00:50,520
semata-mata nak dapatkan
keterangan Lin Xin'er?

21
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,119
Ini...

22
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:53,280
Tak keterlaluan ke?

23
00:00:53,600 --> 00:00:56,000
Datuk buat begini
untuk tutup kes secepat mungkin.

24
00:00:56,039 --> 00:00:57,560
Selagi kes belum ditutup,

25
00:00:58,039 --> 00:01:00,520
Cik Chu kena terus dipenjara.

26
00:01:00,759 --> 00:01:01,600
Kalau begitu,

27
00:01:02,079 --> 00:01:03,320
kalau tiada bukti nyata

28
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:04,920
membuktikan Chang ialah Tupai Jed,

29
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:07,079
dia patut dibebaskan segera.

30
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:08,840
Dan kalau buktinya kukuh,

31
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:11,079
dia patut dihukum pancung di khalayak.

32
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:13,280
Shuang!

33
00:01:13,959 --> 00:01:15,920
Walau kata-kata Lin Xin'er meragukan,

34
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,719
Chu Yunchang tetap
suspek utama.

35
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,599
Daripada ramai yang boleh dia sebut,

36
00:01:19,599 --> 00:01:20,920
kenapa dia pilih Chu Yunchang

37
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:21,920
sebagai Tupai Jed?

38
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,599
Tuduhan melulu
atau dendam peribadi.

39
00:01:23,599 --> 00:01:24,439
Kedua-duanya boleh jadi.

40
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:25,439
Kau...

41
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:27,760
Kau cuma nak bersihkan nama kekasih kau.

42
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:29,640
Chang tak bersalah.

43
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,640
Memang wajar buktikan dia tak bersalah.

44
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:32,760
Tapi...

45
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:35,760
Buyu.

46
00:01:36,239 --> 00:01:38,719
Yang penting sekarang
cari bukti.

47
00:01:39,079 --> 00:01:42,280
Biro Pintu Gerbang takkan
aniaya orang tak bersalah,

48
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:44,280
tapi kami juga takkan
biar penjenayah bebas.

49
00:01:45,620 --> 00:01:47,560
- Faham, Pesuruhjaya.
- Faham, Pesuruhjaya.

50
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:52,439
Buyu.

51
00:01:56,359 --> 00:01:58,040
Kau orang kanan aku.

52
00:01:58,060 --> 00:02:00,040
Yang paling berkebolehan
selalu paling banyak kerja.

53
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:03,319
Ada satu lagi hal
aku nak kau uruskan.

54
00:02:03,319 --> 00:02:04,280
Arahkan saja, Pesuruhjaya.

55
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,840
Aku akan buat sebaiknya.

56
00:02:06,719 --> 00:02:07,480
Datuk!

57
00:02:07,959 --> 00:02:09,000
Datuk kena tolong saya!

58
00:02:09,110 --> 00:02:10,879
Seorang pegawai Datuk di sini
memang keterlaluan.

59
00:02:11,159 --> 00:02:12,560
Dia buli saya sebaik saya sampai!

60
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,479
Dia siap campak saya dalam sel!

61
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:16,439
Datuk mesti hukum dia!

62
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:19,439
Dialah!

63
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:21,439
Yang di situ!

64
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,800
Itulah orangnya, Datuk!

65
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,990
Wuxia, cukup merapu.

66
00:02:24,599 --> 00:02:26,960
Buyu yang terbaik antara kami.

67
00:02:27,199 --> 00:02:28,080
Dengar betul-betul.

68
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,960
Mulai sekarang, dia guru kau.

69
00:02:30,479 --> 00:02:30,800
Saya?

70
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,439
Itulah yang aku nak bincang
dengan kau.

71
00:02:32,639 --> 00:02:33,240
Buyu,

72
00:02:33,719 --> 00:02:34,919
ambil Wuxia jadi anak didik kau.

73
00:02:34,919 --> 00:02:36,240
Latih dia betul-betul, bersungguh-sungguh.

74
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,919
Datuk, jangan! Tunggu!

75
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:40,319
Tak ada hal,

76
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,360
wahai anak murid.

77
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,680
Jauh! Jangan dekat saya!

78
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:51,120
Tak!

79
00:02:52,159 --> 00:02:52,840
Berhenti!

80
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,290
Bukan saya! Saya tak buat!

81
00:02:54,719 --> 00:02:55,400
Bukan saya!

82
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,680
Tolong, biarkan saya!

83
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:04,199
Kau...

84
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:05,080
Jauh dari saya!

85
00:03:08,319 --> 00:03:09,080
Saya merayu.

86
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:09,800
Tolong.

87
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,840
Biar saya tidur, boleh?

88
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:12,199
Saya merayu!

89
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:16,510
Kementerian Kehakiman akan datang
soal siasat kau esok.

90
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:18,639
Masa kita makin suntuk.

91
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,039
Jadi, dengar sini.

92
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:21,680
Kau ada dua pilihan.

93
00:03:21,879 --> 00:03:23,319
Pertama, kau bekerjasama dengan aku.

94
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,159
Atau kedua,

95
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:28,159
mimpi ngeri lebih teruk daripada mati.

96
00:03:33,039 --> 00:03:33,639
Baik.

97
00:03:34,759 --> 00:03:36,319
Tanya apa saja kau nak.

98
00:03:36,319 --> 00:03:37,319
Tapi lepas kau selesai,

99
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,919
kau kena bagi aku tidur sekejap.

100
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:40,879
Setuju.

101
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:42,800
Soalan pertama.

102
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:44,919
Kau pernah nampak Token Suci?

103
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:47,000
Token Suci?

104
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:48,639
Token Suci...

105
00:03:49,919 --> 00:03:51,080
Token Suci...

106
00:03:52,039 --> 00:03:53,159
Aku ingat pernah nampak

107
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:56,000
dengan guru aku masa kecil dulu.

108
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:58,800
Tapi lepas itu aku tak pernah nampak.

109
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:02,080
Yang aku ada cuma replika

110
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:05,680
dibuat Jia Yizhen ikut ingatan aku.

111
00:04:08,159 --> 00:04:09,240
Siapa guru kau?

112
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,800
Guru?

113
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,439
Guru aku...

114
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,520
Guru aku...

115
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:18,160
Tak, tak!

116
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:19,040
Aku tak boleh cakap!

117
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,240
Aku tak boleh cakap apa-apa!

118
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,519
Aku merayu...

119
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,040
Aku merayu, lepaskan aku!

120
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,600
Tolong, lepaskan aku!

121
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,199
Tolong!

122
00:04:25,199 --> 00:04:26,839
Kenapa kau selemah ini?

123
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,839
Kau terlalu rapuh.

124
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,720
Amaran!

125
00:04:34,730 --> 00:04:36,079
Kamu semua terpaku buat apa?

126
00:04:36,079 --> 00:04:37,279
Tangkap pencuri!

127
00:04:37,279 --> 00:04:38,279
Pengawal! Sesiapa!

128
00:04:41,959 --> 00:04:43,160
Perak aku! Semua hilang!

129
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,319
Tupai Jed beraksi lagi!

130
00:04:53,012 --> 00:04:54,012
(Biro Pintu Gerbang, Kementerian Kehakiman)

131
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:54,680
Datuk,

132
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,759
ini mesti kerja
subahatnya.

133
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:57,920
Percayalah cakap saya.

134
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:00,199
Chu Yunchang terkunci dalam sel,

135
00:05:01,079 --> 00:05:03,839
tapi Tupai Jed masih
bebas di Ibu Kota.

136
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,759
Sekarang Lin Xin'er meracau,

137
00:05:05,879 --> 00:05:07,079
Timbalan Menteri akan nampak ini

138
00:05:07,079 --> 00:05:08,240
masa soal siasat

139
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:11,199
dan pasti bebaskan Chu Yunchang.

140
00:05:11,199 --> 00:05:13,079
Jelas ini helah perempuan itu.

141
00:05:13,079 --> 00:05:15,399
Satu bandar dalam keadaan panik,

142
00:05:15,399 --> 00:05:16,879
tapi Datuk masih asyik

143
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:18,360
dengan wanita dalam penjara itu.

144
00:05:18,580 --> 00:05:20,600
Macam mana saya nak
jelaskan pada atasan?

145
00:05:20,839 --> 00:05:21,439
Datuk.

146
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,600
Tolong, beri saya satu lagi peluang.

147
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,680
Chu Yunchang.

148
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,199
Kau Tupai Jed, betul?

149
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,480
Mana bukti kau?

150
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:36,240
Lin Xin'er cam kau sendiri.

151
00:05:37,439 --> 00:05:38,199
Baik.

152
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:41,519
Kalau kau boleh suruh dia cam aku lagi,

153
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:42,800
aku akan mengaku.

154
00:05:44,199 --> 00:05:45,519
Buat dia jadi gila

155
00:05:45,519 --> 00:05:46,560
takkan lepaskan kau.

156
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,040
Hari ini,

157
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:51,560
aku akan dapatkan pengakuan.

158
00:05:52,279 --> 00:05:54,439
Kau nak paksa aku mengaku dengan pukul?

159
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:57,660
Bersalah atau tidak, lepas dipukul baru tahu.

160
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:00,480
Luo Wushuang,

161
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,040
kau tahu akibat

162
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,720
penyeksaan haram?

163
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,639
Dan macam mana nasib kau

164
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,120
lepas aku selesai urus kau?

165
00:06:09,959 --> 00:06:10,639
Buat!

166
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:17,480
Berhenti!

167
00:06:20,199 --> 00:06:21,000
Jangan berani.

168
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,120
Selagi aku ada.

169
00:06:23,439 --> 00:06:24,839
Buyu, jangan halang aku.

170
00:06:25,070 --> 00:06:26,839
Wushuang, kau sedar apa kau buat?

171
00:06:27,399 --> 00:06:29,040
Kau akan dilucutkan pangkat!

172
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:30,279
Kalau aku bagi hasil,

173
00:06:30,279 --> 00:06:31,480
tak ada siapa peduli caranya.

174
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,120
Buat!

175
00:06:35,439 --> 00:06:36,160
Mao Buyu!

176
00:06:36,439 --> 00:06:37,319
Tak ada siapa bergerak!

177
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:39,639
Mao Buyu...

178
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:41,600
Kau betul-betul buat semua ni untuk dia?

179
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:46,199
Wushuang, aku selamatkan kau dari silap yang tak boleh ditebus.

180
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,439
Kalau kau betul-betul peduli aku,

181
00:06:48,439 --> 00:06:49,800
kau takkan halang aku.

182
00:06:51,399 --> 00:06:52,079
Buat!

183
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,279
Buyu!

184
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:08,360
- Yu!
- Buyu!

185
00:07:09,639 --> 00:07:10,319
Buyu!

186
00:07:11,199 --> 00:07:12,720
Macam mana kau boleh sebegitu melulu, Yu?

187
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,279
Lapor!

188
00:07:17,319 --> 00:07:18,120
Pegawai!

189
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:19,480
Ada apa?

190
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,590
Timbalan Menteri Zhou sudah tiba.

191
00:07:28,950 --> 00:07:32,425
(Kementerian Kehakiman)

192
00:07:32,575 --> 00:07:34,600
(Timbalan Menteri Kehakiman)

193
00:07:47,319 --> 00:07:50,639
Bawa masuk banduan Lin Xin'er dan suspek Chu Yunchang.

194
00:08:06,879 --> 00:08:07,600
Lin Xin'er.

195
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,639
Kau dah disabitkan atas jenayah kau.

196
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:12,240
Hari ini kita tak bincang hal itu lagi.

197
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,879
Kau mengenal pasti Chu Yunchang

198
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:17,240
sebagai Tupai Jed, ketua Mazhab Tangan Suci.

199
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,240
Ada bukti?

200
00:08:48,675 --> 00:08:49,625
(MENJUNJUNG UNDANG-UNDANG)

201
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:06,960
Timbalan Menteri.

202
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,679
Banduan itu bunuh diri.

203
00:09:13,639 --> 00:09:15,240
Macam mana kamu urus tempat ini?

204
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:19,159
Kamu bawa orang tak waras untuk aku soal siasat?

205
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,360
Bawa dia keluar.

206
00:09:21,639 --> 00:09:22,159
Baik, tuan.

207
00:09:26,175 --> 00:09:27,950
(MENJUNJUNG UNDANG-UNDANG)

208
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:30,360
Cukup.

209
00:09:31,090 --> 00:09:32,279
Apa lagi bukti yang ada

210
00:09:32,679 --> 00:09:35,159
untuk tuduh Chu Yunchang sebagai Tupai Jed?

211
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:38,759
Tuanku, baru-baru ini saya berlawan satu lawan satu dengan Tupai Jed.

212
00:09:39,159 --> 00:09:40,679
Dia ada kecederaan lama,

213
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:43,399
yang kambuh masa kami bertarung.

214
00:09:43,679 --> 00:09:45,679
Kecederaan Chu Yunchang juga kambuh masa itu.

215
00:09:45,759 --> 00:09:46,840
Ini bukti kukuh.

216
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:48,159
Timbalan Menteri,

217
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:49,320
kecederaan Yunchang

218
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:51,350
disebabkan Li Wan masa dia selamatkan adik saya.

219
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,799
Dia wanita muda yang lemah.

220
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,280
Lepas cedera teruk,

221
00:09:54,559 --> 00:09:55,440
memang biasa

222
00:09:55,799 --> 00:09:56,679
untuk ia kambuh.

223
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,279
Panggil Mao Wenrong.

224
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:00,600
Baik, tuan.

225
00:10:03,639 --> 00:10:04,480
Panggil Mao Wenrong!

226
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:07,960
Timbalan Menteri,

227
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,080
kecederaan Chu Yunchang

228
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:11,960
memang terjadi masa dia selamatkan saya.

229
00:10:12,210 --> 00:10:13,559
Malam di Kediaman Putera Duan,

230
00:10:13,559 --> 00:10:15,159
saya berada di bilik Chu Yunchang sepanjang masa

231
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:15,960
menjaga dia.

232
00:10:16,559 --> 00:10:18,159
Saya tak pernah nampak dia keluar sendiri.

233
00:10:20,159 --> 00:10:20,879
Rong!

234
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,399
Wushuang,

235
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,879
saya cuma cakap yang benar,

236
00:10:23,879 --> 00:10:24,840
tanpa berat sebelah.

237
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:27,919
Walau saya tak suka Chu Yunchang seratus kali pun,

238
00:10:28,399 --> 00:10:29,879
saya takkan fitnah dia.

239
00:10:33,519 --> 00:10:34,440
Dengar keputusan.

240
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:37,200
Banduan Lin Xin'er telah bunuh diri.

241
00:10:38,412 --> 00:10:39,971
Kenal pasti mayat dan tutup kes.

242
00:10:42,350 --> 00:10:44,520
Bukti tak cukup untuk sabitkan Chu Yunchang.

243
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:46,519
Dia dibebaskan.

244
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:50,240
Luo Wushuang,

245
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:54,399
kau berani tahan orang awam tanpa bukti

246
00:10:54,399 --> 00:10:56,840
dan jadikan kes ini tunggang-langgang.

247
00:10:57,399 --> 00:10:59,000
Kau memang bodoh dan melulu.

248
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:00,480
Lapor diri ke Kor Personel.

249
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,360
Kau diturunkan pangkat.

250
00:11:03,062 --> 00:11:03,799
Timbalan Menteri...

251
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,080
Dengar dulu...

252
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:06,440
Diam!

253
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:12,240
Tupai Jed dah mengganas di Ibu Kota berhari-hari,

254
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:15,240
merompak banyak rumah bangsawan.

255
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:17,120
Kamu tak boleh tangkap pencuri sebenar,

256
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:19,879
jadi kamu jadikan gadis muda itu kambing hitam?

257
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,360
Keterlaluan!

258
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:24,399
Aku arahkan kamu tangkap Tupai Jed yang sebenar

259
00:11:24,639 --> 00:11:26,559
dalam seratus hari.

260
00:11:27,399 --> 00:11:28,639
Kalau kamu cuba perdaya aku

261
00:11:28,639 --> 00:11:30,000
dengan palsu lagi...

262
00:11:34,759 --> 00:11:35,639
Pesuruhjaya Luo,

263
00:11:37,879 --> 00:11:40,080
kamu juga akan menanggung kesalahan.

264
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:41,840
Faham.

265
00:11:44,770 --> 00:11:45,559
Timbalan Menteri Zhou!

266
00:11:45,559 --> 00:11:46,200
Wushuang!

267
00:11:58,600 --> 00:11:59,200
Chang.

268
00:11:59,879 --> 00:12:00,799
Tangan kau okey?

269
00:12:04,919 --> 00:12:05,480
Kenapa?

270
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:08,320
Masih rasa tak puas hati?

271
00:12:11,700 --> 00:12:13,840
Ini salah aku sebab gagal cari bukti nyata.

272
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:16,960
Sebab aku, Chu Yunchang terlepas.

273
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:20,080
Nah.

274
00:12:21,399 --> 00:12:22,080
Rasa sikit.

275
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,480
Aku dah kata kau melulu.

276
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,480
Kau masih tak berubah.

277
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:33,720
Patutlah kau kena tipu lagi.

278
00:12:34,039 --> 00:12:34,639
Datuk...

279
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,679
Datuk pun rasa Chu Yunchang

280
00:12:36,679 --> 00:12:37,500
mencurigakan juga?

281
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:41,080
Datuk terlalu berlembut dengan wanita ini.

282
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,840
Sebab kamu benar-benar syak dia,

283
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,679
atau sebab Mao Buyu?

284
00:12:48,559 --> 00:12:49,480
Dua-dua.

285
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:50,720
Dari segi tugas,

286
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,360
walau dia bukan Tupai Jed,

287
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:53,960
dia pasti
dengan Mazhab Tangan Suci.

288
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,720
Dia musuh ketat Biro Pintu kita.

289
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:56,919
Dan secara peribadi,

290
00:12:56,919 --> 00:12:58,840
Datuk, Datuk tahu pendirian saya.

291
00:12:59,679 --> 00:13:01,679
Kalau saya tak suka Mao Buyu,

292
00:13:01,919 --> 00:13:03,960
saya takkan setuju
temu janji buta itu.

293
00:13:04,759 --> 00:13:07,039
Saya dan Buyu setaraf.

294
00:13:07,039 --> 00:13:07,960
Memang sepadan.

295
00:13:08,399 --> 00:13:10,840
Jadi saya takkan biar orang luar meragukan

296
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:12,679
datang perbodohkan dia.

297
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,279
Jadi, demi tugas dan cinta,

298
00:13:17,679 --> 00:13:19,840
kamu tak mahu lepaskan gadis Chu itu.

299
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:20,960
Ya.

300
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:22,480
Bagus.

301
00:13:23,279 --> 00:13:25,320
Kalau begitu, kamu kena lebih berhati-hati.

302
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:27,720
Kalau kamu benar-benar percaya Chu Yunchang

303
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,200
ialah Tupai Jed,

304
00:13:29,399 --> 00:13:30,320
maka kamu berdepan

305
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:33,559
mahaguru baharu yang diiktiraf dunia.

306
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,120
Kamu betul-betul fikir

307
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:37,360
dia akan biar kamu tangkap semudah itu?

308
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:39,320
Kali ini saya terlalu tak sabar.

309
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:41,480
Macam teh dalam tangan kamu.

310
00:13:42,039 --> 00:13:43,360
Kamu takkan tahu sama ada ia betul-betul

311
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:44,440
campuran yang sedap

312
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:46,639
hingga kamu habiskan sampai ke dasar.

313
00:13:55,879 --> 00:13:56,879
Chang, kenapa?

314
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:57,960
Tak ada apa-apa.

315
00:13:58,879 --> 00:13:59,480
Chang...

316
00:14:02,240 --> 00:14:04,000
Jelas kamu tak nampak "ok".

317
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:09,600
Aku tak sangka Luo Wushuang
terlalu taksub dengan kamu.

318
00:14:14,399 --> 00:14:16,200
Itu yang ganggu kamu?

319
00:14:16,559 --> 00:14:17,879
Itu tak macam kamu langsung.

320
00:14:18,310 --> 00:14:19,600
Hanya kamu yang faham aku.

321
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,360
Mestilah.

322
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:25,559
Tak kira apa orang kata,

323
00:14:25,559 --> 00:14:27,279
aku tetap percaya kamu.

324
00:14:27,399 --> 00:14:28,639
Bukan aku naif

325
00:14:28,639 --> 00:14:29,720
atau tak pandai menilai.

326
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:30,879
Cuma...

327
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,840
Aku kenal Chang aku,

328
00:14:33,840 --> 00:14:35,360
mustahil jadi penjahat kejam.

329
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:37,960
Jadi apa pun alasan kamu,

330
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:38,960
kamu boleh beritahu aku.

331
00:14:41,537 --> 00:14:42,712
(Kedai Bunga Yunchang)

332
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,000
Sakit tak?

333
00:14:49,039 --> 00:14:49,679
Tak.

334
00:14:49,700 --> 00:14:50,480
Cuma luka calar.

335
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:53,440
Aku cakap kali terakhir.

336
00:14:54,639 --> 00:14:56,840
Walau kamu lindungi
Tupai Jed,

337
00:14:57,279 --> 00:14:58,519
sebab kamu terhutang budi dengannya,

338
00:14:58,759 --> 00:14:59,679
aku tak kisah.

339
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:02,519
Kita hadapi masa lalu bersama,

340
00:15:02,519 --> 00:15:03,600
dan kita akan urus

341
00:15:03,799 --> 00:15:05,559
apa pun yang menanti di masa depan.

342
00:15:06,399 --> 00:15:07,000
Tapi...

343
00:15:08,039 --> 00:15:09,399
kamu kena janji satu benda.

344
00:15:15,912 --> 00:15:19,187
♪Dendam dan sesal
bagai arak keras♪

345
00:15:19,225 --> 00:15:22,100
♪Teguk habis, lepaskanlah♪

346
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:28,318
♪Cawan kosong untuk cinta dan benci♪

347
00:15:29,500 --> 00:15:32,820
♪Air mata kaburkan takdir yang tak mampu ku kawal♪

348
00:15:32,950 --> 00:15:35,870
♪Mari minum sampai fajar♪

349
00:15:37,038 --> 00:15:42,278
♪Di balik topeng ini, aku takkan menipu♪

350
00:15:43,500 --> 00:15:45,893
♪Setiap pertemuan semula terasa seperti pertama kali♪

351
00:15:45,893 --> 00:15:49,543
♪Senyum tersembunyi ini takkan pudar♪

352
00:15:49,612 --> 00:15:53,102
♪Satu hati, setia di sisimu♪

353
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:56,175
♪Hingga ke hujung waktu♪

354
00:15:56,175 --> 00:15:59,550
♪Bulan menelusuri wajahmu♪

355
00:15:59,737 --> 00:16:03,325
♪Diselubungi awan, kamu penuhi hatiku♪

356
00:16:03,325 --> 00:16:09,565
♪Mencari kamu
dan menunaikan janji kita selamanya♪

357
00:16:09,900 --> 00:16:13,115
♪Doa senyap dalam jiwaku♪

358
00:16:13,400 --> 00:16:16,938
♪Mendukung sumpahku di bawah bulan♪

359
00:16:17,225 --> 00:16:20,250
♪Moga kita takkan terpisah lagi♪

360
00:16:20,250 --> 00:16:23,350
♪Menuju selamanya♪

361
00:16:23,350 --> 00:16:27,200
♪Bulan menelusuri wajahmu♪

362
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:30,560
♪Diselubungi awan, kamu penuhi hatiku♪

363
00:16:30,750 --> 00:16:36,710
♪Mencari kamu
dan menunaikan janji kita selamanya♪

364
00:16:37,787 --> 00:16:47,427
♪Hanya untuk bersamamu♪

